# Results folders - 只忽略模型权重，允许实验结果文件自动跟踪
# 常见模型权重格式
**/results/*.pth      # PyTorch
**/results/*.pt       # PyTorch (另一种扩展名)
**/results/*.pkl      # Pickle序列化
**/results/*.h5       # Keras/TensorFlow
**/results/*.hdf5     # HDF5格式
**/results/*.ckpt     # TensorFlow checkpoints
**/results/*.safetensors  # HuggingFace Safetensors
**/results/*.bin      # 二进制模型文件
**/results/*.model    # 通用模型文件
# JSON/CSV/TXT/PNG等实验记录文件会自动被跟踪

